{"id":2359492,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"菲鲁兹·蓝是日本的女性声优。\n\n出生于东京，父亲是埃及人，母亲是日本人。\n\n小学5年级中途开始直到小学毕业都住在埃及开罗。\n\n初中时读了漫画《JOJO的奇妙冒险 石之海》，并以此为契机参加了Skype上的JOJO朗读会，在朗读的过程中产生了成为JOJO声优的想法。\n\n由于双亲的反对，她在高中毕业后进入了平面设计的专科学校，但最终还是希望进入声优养成所，在担任了1年的牙科助手后进入Pro·Fit声优养成所，毕业后加入Pro·Fit事务所。\n\n2019年在《流汗吧!健身少女》中首次主演。","name":"菲鲁兹·蓝","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Fairouz Ai (ファイルーズあい, Fairūzu Ai), born as Fairouz Ai Kadota (門田ファイルーズあい, Kadota Fairūzu Ai), is a Japanese voice actress. She was born in Tokyo, Japan, to a Japanese mother and an Egyptian father.","name":"Fairouz Ai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"菲魯茲·藍是日本的女性聲優。出身於東京都，父親是埃及人、母親是日本人，畢業於 Pro-Fit 聲優養成所，所屬公司為 Mausu Promotion。","name":"菲魯茲·藍","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ファイルーズあい","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"파이루즈 아이","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Fairouz Ai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Fairouz Ai (ファイルーズあい, Fairūzu Ai), nacida como Fairouz Ai Kadota (門田ファイルーズあい, Kadota Fairūzu Ai), es una actriz de voz japonesa de Tokio, Japón. Es hija de madre japonesa y padre egipcio.","name":"Fairouz Ai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Fairouz Ai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ฟัยรูซ ไอ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","